
Kth Bit:
Get: x & (1<<k) != 0
Set: x |= (1 << k)
Unset: x &= ~(1 << k)
Toggle: x ^= (1 << k)

Rightmost set Bit:
Get: x & -x
Unset: x &= ~(x&-x)

Rightmost unset Bit:
Get: ~n & (n+1)
Set: n |= ~n & (n+1)

Check if number is power of 2:
x == x&-x
x & x-1 == 0

Two's complement of x, i.e. -x = ~(x-1) = ~x+1
Unset lowest set bit: x & (x-1)



